COMPONENT NAME: IKM SQL to Siebel Append (EIM) COMPONENT VERSION: 10.1.3.1 AUTHOR: Oracle COMPATIBILITY: ODI 10.1.3.5.0 and above
Description: - Integration Knowledge Module - Integrates data into a Siebel EIM (Enterprise Integration Manager) table from any ANSI-SQL92 compliant staging area, then generate the appropriate EIM configuration files (.ifb) and runs the import process using the server Manager. The target table is populated in truncate / insert mode
Restriction: - This module require srvrmgr on the machine where the agent runs.
Automatically attempts to insert data into the Target Datastore of the Interface
Check this option if you wish to truncate the target datastore.
Check this option if you wish to delete all the rows of the target datastore.
Path to create the EIM configuration files (.ifb). This parameter is mandatory.
Path to the srvrmgr binary. This parameter is mandatory.
Network address of the Gateway Server machine. This parameter is mandatory.
Enterprise Server name. This parameter is mandatory.
Siebel Server name (default is all servers). This parameter is mandatory.
Server administrator user name. This parameter is mandatory.
Server administrator password. This parameter is mandatory.

<% if ("C".equals(odiRef.getJrnInfo( "JRN_METHOD"))) { %> /* Consistant journalization detected. */ /* Lock should be done by a specific step in a package */ <% } else { %> update <%=odiRef.getTable( "L" , "JRN_NAME" , "A" )%> set JRN_CONSUMED = '1' where (1=1) <%=odiRef.getJrnFilter()%> <% } %>

import os # #Mandatory Option # SIEBEL_GATEWAY = '<%=odiRef.getOption("SIEBEL_GATEWAY")%>' SIEBEL_ENTERPRISE = '<%=odiRef.getOption("SIEBEL_ENTERPRISE")%>' SIEBEL_SERVER = '<%=snpRef.getOption("SIEBEL_SERVER")%>' SERVER_USER = '<%=odiRef.getOption("SERVER_USER")%>' SERVER_USER_PWD = '<%=odiRef.getOption("SERVER_USER_PWD")%>' SRVRMGR_PATH =r'<%=odiRef.getOption("SRVRMGR_PATH")%>' IFB_PATH =r'<%=odiRef.getOption("IFB_PATH")%>' TABLE_NAME = '<%=odiRef.getTargetTable("TABLE_NAME")%>' STARTTASK = r'run task for component eim with config=%s/%s_IMPORT.ifb , TraceFlags=1, ErrorFlags=1, SQLFlags=8' %( IFB_PATH, TABLE_NAME)
cmd = '''%s/SRVRMGR -g %s -e %s -s %s -u %s -p %s -c "%s" ''' %(SRVRMGR_PATH,SIEBEL_GATEWAY, SIEBEL_ENTERPRISE, SIEBEL_SERVER, SERVER_USER, SERVER_USER_PWD, STARTTASK) if os.system(cmd) <> 0 : raise "SRVRMGR error", "Error executing OS command: %s" %cmd

insert into <%=odiRef.getTable("L","TARG_NAME","A")%> ( <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "((INS and !TRG) and REW)")%> <%=odiRef.getColList(",", "[COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "((INS and TRG) and REW)")%> ) values ( <%=odiRef.getColList("", ":[CX_COL_NAME]", ",
	", "", "((INS and !TRG) and REW)")%> <%=odiRef.getColList(",
	", "[EXPRESSION]", ",
	", "", "((INS and TRG) and REW)")%> )

select <%=odiRef.getPop("DISTINCT_ROWS")%> <%=odiRef.getColList("", "[EXPRESSION]\t[ALIAS_SEP] [CX_COL_NAME]", ",\n\t", "", "((INS and !TRG) and REW)")%> from <%=odiRef.getFrom()%> where <% if (odiRef.getPop("HAS_JRN").equals("0")) { %> (1=1) <%} else {%> not (JRN_FLAG = 'D') <% } %> <%=odiRef.getJoin()%> <%=odiRef.getFilter()%> <%=odiRef.getJrnFilter() %> <%=odiRef.getGrpBy()%> <%=odiRef.getHaving()%>

<% if ("C".equals(odiRef.getJrnInfo( "JRN_METHOD"))) { %> /* Consistant journalization detected. */ /* Lock should be done by a specific step in a package */ <% } else { %> delete from <%=odiRef.getTable("L","JRN_NAME","A")%> where JRN_CONSUMED = '1' <%=odiRef.getJrnFilter()%> <% } %>
